	</tbody>
</table>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:18px;"><strong>Temperatures</strong></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:16px;">The difference in average seasonal temperature between El Ni&ntilde;o, ENSO-neutral, and La Ni&ntilde;a winters is not especially large.&nbsp; In general, El Ni&ntilde;o winters are slightly cooler than either La Ni&ntilde;a or neutral winters for local cities.</span></p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width: 760px;">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</td>
